instructionText: Look for a circular shape and indicate if it is present or absent in the array. If it is present press 'p' and if absent press 'a'. Press SPACE to start.
Look for green vertical bar (target) and indicate if it is present or absent in the array. If green vertical target is present press 'p' and if absent press 'a'. Press SPACE to start.
Look for a line tilted 45 degrees to the right (target) and indicate if it is present or absent in the array. If the target is present press 'p' and if absent press 'a'. Press SPACE to start.
